to:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE1MzE0/bullying-2.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eTennessee lawmakers a year ago laid out a legal definition of what constitutes bullying. Now, they’ve given that definition teeth. Anyone convicted in juvenile court of a bullying offense occurring on or after July 1, 2025 will have their driver’s license suspended for a full year. If it’s a first offense, a bully can apply to get a restricted license – but it can only be used to school, work or religious services. Forget social events. And if you’re in an after-school program, including sports? Forget it. Catch the bus or get a ride with your parents or friends.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"will-it-work\"\u003eWill it Work?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003e“Taking away driving privileges will hopefully get the attention of bullies and deter them from being mean to others,” said State Rep. Russell.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"For teens, a driver\u0026#39;s license is a critical rite of passage.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3863\" height=\"2578\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 16w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 32w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 48w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 64w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 96w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 128w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 256w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 384w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 750w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 828w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 1200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 1920w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 2048w, https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA 3840w\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/thearenagroup-prod/images/w_3863,h_2578,c_scale/v1739271903/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw/MjA5MTMwNzgxOTIyNTAyNTAw.jpg?_i=AA\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eNot everyone is convinced, however. It may only help with those bullies who are caught and prosecuted. And it doesn’t deal with bullies too young to drive, some skeptics warned. It’s going to take intervention long before that, suggested Scott Payne, a manager for Contact Care Line, a Knoxville-based social services organization, in an \u003ca href=\"https://www.wvlt.tv/2025/07/01/hopefully-prevent-tragic-events-new-tn-law-suspending-teens-driving-privileges-bullying/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003einterview \u003c/a\u003ewith Knoxville TV station WVLT. “Bullies aren’t just born. They don’t just pop up. They’re products of their environment. So we need to be talking with them and finding out what’s going on in their lives that’s bringing about this type of behavior from them.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eAbout the Author\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"100px\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk4NTg5/1747774662839blob.jpg 828w, https://www.au